00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 65 =

20
00:01:41,100 --> 00:01:42,980
Mr. Zhang. Mr. Liang.

21
00:01:48,020 --> 00:01:51,220
= Liang Quanyi =
Huaiji, I come to say goodbye.

22
00:01:52,540 --> 00:01:53,980
