35
00:02:30,300 --> 00:02:32,340
Mr. Liang, I’m sorry.

36
00:02:34,100 --> 00:02:36,420
I knew Princess didn’t get well
with Prince Consort,

37
00:02:36,500 --> 00:02:38,020
