38
00:02:38,420 --> 00:02:39,100
In case of problem,

39
00:02:39,100 --> 00:02:40,780
I hid the truth.

40
00:02:40,980 --> 00:02:43,020
I truly failed my job.

41
00:02:44,220 --> 00:02:45,180
I’m punished.

42
00:02:47,180 --> 00:02:48,180
Yet I’m convinced.

43
00:02:54,700 --> 00:02:55,500
But you...

44
00:03:01,180 --> 00:03:02,100
I don’t like to

45
00:03:03,180 --> 00:03:04,180
