57
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:14,840
at every moment.

58
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:17,600
She’s the princess

59
00:04:18,520 --> 00:04:20,360
that the most honorable man

60
00:04:20,360 --> 00:04:21,880
