62
00:04:26,400 --> 00:04:27,680
But you...

63
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:31,000
Don’t you know?

64
00:04:35,840 --> 00:04:38,320
Why didn’t you keep distance from her?

65
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:45,320
For Princess,

66
00:04:47,320 --> 00:04:48,360
when she left the palace,

67
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:52,200
