70
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:01,240
where there was no hope.

71
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:07,800
I can’t help her.

72
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:11,880
But I couldn’t help walking to her

73
00:05:13,440 --> 00:05:14,760
and be her driftwood

74
00:05:18,400 --> 00:05:19,800
so that she wouldn’t

75
00:05:21,400 --> 00:05:22,360
