89
00:05:58,580 --> 00:06:00,180
How dare you criticize officials?

90
00:06:06,780 --> 00:06:08,300
You still don’t know you’re wrong.

91
00:06:09,980 --> 00:06:11,140
At your age,

92
00:06:12,300 --> 00:06:14,500
