93
00:06:16,820 --> 00:06:17,580
Ren Shouzhong

94
00:06:19,340 --> 00:06:21,220
interfered with Princess’s family affair,

95
00:06:22,100 --> 00:06:24,900
bullied Prince Consort and criticized officials.

96
00:06:25,900 --> 00:06:27,140
Considering he has been

97
00:06:27,740 --> 00:06:29,100
