102
00:06:41,100 --> 00:06:42,300
I realized my fault.

103
00:06:50,100 --> 00:06:52,140
Everyone, you’ve been working for years.

104
00:06:53,980 --> 00:06:55,060
You’re of high position.

105
00:06:56,140 --> 00:06:58,020
More and more people flatter you.

106
00:06:59,060 --> 00:07:00,780
Few people reprimand you

107
00:07:00,780 --> 00:07:01,940
