118
00:08:00,910 --> 00:08:02,250
Don’t punish him.”

119
00:09:07,220 --> 00:09:07,980
There you are.

120
00:09:37,490 --> 00:09:38,180
Look.

121
00:09:39,580 --> 00:09:40,780
