128
00:10:04,020 --> 00:10:04,940
When I let it go,

129
00:10:15,140 --> 00:10:16,180
without my restraint,

130
00:10:17,820 --> 00:10:18,940
it will also

131
00:10:18,940 --> 00:10:21,620
crawl to

132
00:10:23,420 --> 00:10:24,660
