137
00:10:39,700 --> 00:10:42,500
Your Majesty. It’s cold on the ground.

138
00:10:44,180 --> 00:10:45,260
Your legs will hurt.

139
00:11:04,340 --> 00:11:05,780
It’s been nearly 30 years.

140
00:11:10,420 --> 00:11:12,780
The Empress Dowager has passed away for 30 years.

141
00:11:23,140 --> 00:11:25,060
Back then, she sat here

142
00:11:27,780 --> 00:11:28,700
and told me

143
00:11:31,420 --> 00:11:32,340
I couldn’t marry

144
00:11:32,340 --> 00:11:33,980
