146
00:11:38,420 --> 00:11:39,500
She said I should marry

147
00:11:40,660 --> 00:11:43,900
Governor Guo Chong’s granddaughter.

148
00:11:45,500 --> 00:11:47,060
She married the girl I loved

149
00:11:48,380 --> 00:11:50,060
