156
00:12:17,060 --> 00:12:19,180
When I think about it now,

157
00:12:22,220 --> 00:12:23,140
I realized

158
00:12:26,220 --> 00:12:27,140
Miss Guo was truly

159
00:12:27,140 --> 00:12:28,740
