168
00:13:49,020 --> 00:13:50,380
But I know.

169
00:13:51,940 --> 00:13:52,860
Huaiji...

170
00:13:55,340 --> 00:13:56,380
He only wants to

171
00:13:56,380 --> 00:13:57,780
protect Huirou.

172
00:14:09,900 --> 00:14:11,660
Her Highness, here comes Princess.

173
00:14:17,620 --> 00:14:20,860
Her Highness, finally you agree to see me.

174
00:14:21,980 --> 00:14:22,780
Leave us.

175
00:14:23,380 --> 00:14:24,060
Aye.

176
00:14:36,340 --> 00:14:37,540
You are more thoughtful that

177
00:14:39,540 --> 00:14:40,540
you didn’t make more trouble.

178
00:14:47,780 --> 00:14:48,740
Where’s Huaiji?

179
00:14:51,300 --> 00:14:52,060
Recently, I’ve been

180
00:14:52,060 --> 00:14:53,460
sleeping well and eating regularly.

181
00:14:54,300 --> 00:14:54,940
Father.

182
00:14:55,980 --> 00:14:57,180
Father promised me that

183
00:14:57,900 --> 00:14:59,300
when I was doing fine,

184
00:14:59,500 --> 00:15:01,060
