198
00:16:13,260 --> 00:16:16,140
The Ritual Department will take care of it.

199
00:16:19,460 --> 00:16:20,260
Your Majesty.

200
00:16:20,980 --> 00:16:22,940
In my opinion,

201
00:16:22,980 --> 00:16:23,980
you shouldn’t make

202
00:16:24,100 --> 00:16:25,900
a young eunuch

203
00:16:25,900 --> 00:16:26,860
