207
00:16:30,940 --> 00:16:32,500
He’s even coquettish.

208
00:16:37,100 --> 00:16:38,940
Liang Huaiji worked for me since he was little.

209
00:16:40,580 --> 00:16:43,580
He’s young, but always behaves himself.

210
00:16:44,820 --> 00:16:47,500
I know he’s more knowledgeable and honest

211
00:16:47,860 --> 00:16:49,820
