215
00:17:17,060 --> 00:17:18,740
Your Majesty, hope you can perceive it.

216
00:17:20,860 --> 00:17:22,660
I hear Liang Huaiji didn’t wear the eunuch uniform

217
00:17:22,660 --> 00:17:23,940
in Princess’s Mansion.

218
00:17:24,300 --> 00:17:26,380
= Sima Guang, courtesy name Junshi =
He claimed to be Prince Consort to strangers,

219
00:17:27,580 --> 00:17:29,340
drove a wedge between Princess and Prince Consort

220
00:17:29,580 --> 00:17:31,220
