221
00:17:31,460 --> 00:17:33,780
Is that true?

222
00:17:37,060 --> 00:17:39,140
If it’s true that

223
00:17:39,340 --> 00:17:40,620
Liang Huaiji didn’t wear the eunuch uniform

224
00:17:40,620 --> 00:17:42,140
and made people think he was Prince Consort,

225
00:17:42,900 --> 00:17:45,780
