226
00:17:46,580 --> 00:17:47,500
Your Majesty,

227
00:17:48,340 --> 00:17:50,380
even you’re duped by him.

228
00:17:50,500 --> 00:17:52,500
He’s incredibly good at

229
00:17:52,620 --> 00:17:53,860
cheating people.

230
00:17:55,660 --> 00:17:57,740
How can you not

231
00:17:58,780 --> 00:18:00,300
punish such a sinister man

232
00:18:00,500 --> 00:18:02,700
to defend imperial rules?

233
00:18:06,580 --> 00:18:07,300
Huirou.

234
00:18:14,140 --> 00:18:14,860
Your Highness.

235
00:18:25,700 --> 00:18:27,140
Is it true that

236
00:18:27,460 --> 00:18:28,420
Huaiji didn’t wear the eunuch uniform?

237
00:18:32,460 --> 00:18:33,140
Yes.

238
00:18:34,700 --> 00:18:35,340
But...

239
00:18:37,180 --> 00:18:38,380
But I forced him.

240
00:18:40,780 --> 00:18:42,620
Someone saw that?

241
00:18:44,860 --> 00:18:47,420
Yes.

242
00:18:49,420 --> 00:18:52,740
We were in the Great Xiangguo temple.

243
00:18:54,260 --> 00:18:55,020
In a restaurant.

244
00:18:58,940 --> 00:19:01,420
I just thought

245
00:19:02,180 --> 00:19:05,460
he looked cool in a robe of scholars.

246
00:19:07,900 --> 00:19:08,860
Did someone take him

247
00:19:08,860 --> 00:19:10,140
as Prince Consort by mistake?

248
00:19:14,060 --> 00:19:14,940
After that,

249
00:19:15,660 --> 00:19:17,240
