250
00:19:17,240 --> 00:19:18,070
in the robe of scholars?

251
00:19:25,700 --> 00:19:26,620
What a fool!

252
00:19:33,300 --> 00:19:34,300
You saw that.

253
00:19:35,870 --> 00:19:37,500
Your father sacrificed himself

254
00:19:37,980 --> 00:19:39,020
to stop the censors from

255
00:19:39,020 --> 00:19:40,420
complaining about Huaiji.

256
00:19:41,380 --> 00:19:42,460
But you...

257
00:19:43,580 --> 00:19:45,340
you’ve already given

258
00:19:45,340 --> 00:19:46,380
the solid evidence to others.

259
00:19:47,260 --> 00:19:47,860
No.

260
00:19:48,700 --> 00:19:49,420
No.

261
00:19:50,140 --> 00:19:51,460
Huaiji is innocent.

262
00:19:52,300 --> 00:19:53,620
He’s innocent.

263
00:19:55,660 --> 00:19:56,380
Your Highness.

264
00:19:57,580 --> 00:19:59,060
What will they do with Huaiji?

265
00:20:00,580 --> 00:20:02,220
Will they force Father to kill him?

266
00:20:03,660 --> 00:20:04,700
Ask Father

267
00:20:05,100 --> 00:20:06,740
