268
00:20:06,780 --> 00:20:08,460
and they will no longer complain.

269
00:20:08,460 --> 00:20:09,300
Huirou.

270
00:20:11,420 --> 00:20:12,780
Your father is the Emperor.

271
00:20:13,700 --> 00:20:15,020
