286
00:21:27,300 --> 00:21:28,100
I’ll correct myself.

287
00:21:31,220 --> 00:21:32,820
Please let go of Huaiji.

288
00:21:35,340 --> 00:21:37,220
If you promise me you won’t kill him,

289
00:21:39,100 --> 00:21:40,700
I will go back to my mansion.

290
00:21:43,140 --> 00:21:46,020
Whatever Li Wei and his mother say,

291
00:21:48,100 --> 00:21:49,900
I won’t argue with them again.

292
00:22:11,620 --> 00:22:12,700
I promise you

293
00:22:14,060 --> 00:22:15,580
I won’t kill Huaiji.

294
00:22:16,180 --> 00:22:17,380
Rest assured.

295
00:22:19,020 --> 00:22:19,860
Really?

296
00:22:23,500 --> 00:22:24,340
Tomorrow,

297
00:22:25,140 --> 00:22:27,100
I’ll let him send you back to your mansion.

298
00:22:59,060 --> 00:23:01,020
I promised Huirou not to kill you.

299
00:23:01,940 --> 00:23:03,500
But I must punish you

300
00:23:03,500 --> 00:23:04,900
to convince censors.

301
00:23:06,300 --> 00:23:07,340
Otherwise,

302
00:23:08,580 --> 00:23:09,660
they may soon

303
00:23:09,660 --> 00:23:11,060
come up with a lot of evidence

304
00:23:11,820 --> 00:23:14,180
to challenge Huirou’s morality again.

305
00:23:17,700 --> 00:23:18,460
Aye.

306
00:23:20,860 --> 00:23:22,140
Tomorrow, I’ll give an order,

307
00:23:23,060 --> 00:23:24,500
banishing you from the Capital

308
00:23:25,180 --> 00:23:26,660
to the maintenance team in Luoyang.

309
00:23:37,700 --> 00:23:39,100
Before you leave,

310
00:23:40,220 --> 00:23:41,620
do you have any wish?

311
00:23:46,460 --> 00:23:47,380
I only hope

312
00:23:49,620 --> 00:23:51,380
Princess won’t see me off.

313
00:23:58,020 --> 00:24:03,120
= Stable people make up a peaceful country. =

314
00:24:03,120 --> 00:24:03,860
Come in, please.

315
00:24:05,740 --> 00:24:06,500
One more time.

316
00:24:20,380 --> 00:24:21,060
Stuffed buns.

317
00:24:22,210 --> 00:24:22,940
Stuffed buns.

318
00:24:42,540 --> 00:24:43,380
Huaiji.

319
00:24:43,900 --> 00:24:44,860
Where are you going?

320
00:24:57,340 --> 00:24:59,740
Princess, I want to buy some roasted port

321
00:24:59,980 --> 00:25:01,380
in the Great Xiangguo temple.

322
00:25:02,340 --> 00:25:04,260
It does taste good.

323
00:25:05,340 --> 00:25:06,380
If you want some,

324
00:25:06,900 --> 00:25:08,260
you don’t need to go personally.

325
00:25:09,020 --> 00:25:10,500
It makes no difference

326
00:25:10,740 --> 00:25:11,780
if you ask a eunuch to go for you.

327
00:25:13,540 --> 00:25:14,340
It does.

328
00:25:15,140 --> 00:25:16,500
They don’t know

329
00:25:16,980 --> 00:25:18,540
which part is the best.

330
00:25:18,960 --> 00:25:19,900
They can’t pick the right part.

331
00:25:21,100 --> 00:25:23,660
All right. Go ahead.

332
00:25:25,140 --> 00:25:27,060
But the sky looks dim.

333
00:25:27,220 --> 00:25:28,420
Seems like it’s going to rain.

334
00:25:28,700 --> 00:25:29,940
Come back early

335
00:25:30,100 --> 00:25:31,620
and catch up with me.

336
00:25:33,900 --> 00:25:36,020
I don’t want fat. I want lean meat.

337
00:25:37,500 --> 00:25:39,460
But lean meat isn’t the best.

338
00:25:39,780 --> 00:25:41,540
It tastes better with fat.

339
00:25:42,340 --> 00:25:44,660
But it’ll make me fat.

340
00:26:42,980 --> 00:26:43,780
Officer.

341
00:26:44,580 --> 00:26:45,860
You want roasted pork?

342
00:26:46,260 --> 00:26:46,900
Look.

343
00:26:47,700 --> 00:26:49,100
I just roasted some.

344
00:26:49,100 --> 00:26:50,100
It’s still hot.

345
00:26:57,660 --> 00:26:59,020
Pick some by yourself.

346
00:27:03,700 --> 00:27:04,660
I’ll take this piece.

347
00:27:05,020 --> 00:27:05,660
Okay.

348
00:27:05,660 --> 00:27:06,380
Lean meat.

349
00:27:06,380 --> 00:27:07,220
Okay.

350
00:27:23,130 --> 00:27:24,210
Mr. Zhang.

351
00:27:24,610 --> 00:27:26,170
Please take the roasted pork

352
00:27:27,010 --> 00:27:28,050
to Princess.

353
00:27:54,320 --> 00:27:54,860
Hya.

354
00:27:59,310 --> 00:28:00,940
Hya.

355
00:28:01,570 --> 00:28:05,280
♪ I write a romantic poem in memory of the past ♪

356
00:28:05,280 --> 00:28:08,860
♪ With the love in my heart ♪

357
00:28:08,860 --> 00:28:15,960
♪ I can’t go further unless I’m not obsessive ♪

358
00:28:15,960 --> 00:28:19,650
♪ I live a common life ♪

359
00:28:19,650 --> 00:28:23,880
♪ And experience all feelings ♪

360
00:28:23,880 --> 00:28:30,250
♪ I’m used to having you around me ♪

361
00:28:30,250 --> 00:28:33,940
♪ I write a romantic poem in memory of the past ♪

362
00:28:33,940 --> 00:28:37,400
♪ With the love in my heart ♪

363
00:28:37,400 --> 00:28:44,580
♪ I can’t go further unless I’m not obsessive ♪

364
00:28:44,580 --> 00:28:48,210
♪ I live a common life ♪

365
00:28:48,210 --> 00:28:50,550
♪ And experience all feelings ♪

366
00:28:50,650 --> 00:28:54,130
Huirou, you’re also in my heart.

367
00:28:54,130 --> 00:28:59,400
♪ I’m used to having you around me ♪

368
00:28:59,780 --> 00:29:09,090
♪ I’m used to having you around me ♪

369
00:29:09,450 --> 00:29:10,060
Hya.

370
00:29:10,890 --> 00:29:11,440
Hya.

371
00:29:15,620 --> 00:29:16,020
Hya.

372
00:29:16,740 --> 00:29:17,260
Hya.

373
00:29:22,820 --> 00:29:27,580
= Luoyang =

374
00:29:48,060 --> 00:29:49,100
Here we are.

375
00:30:18,420 --> 00:30:19,280
Princess...

376
00:30:20,970 --> 00:30:22,160
Did she eat nothing again?

377
00:30:27,090 --> 00:30:27,950
Princess asked us

378
00:30:28,340 --> 00:30:29,810
to roast some sweet potatoes.

379
00:30:31,040 --> 00:30:31,860
Sweet potatoes?

380
00:30:36,190 --> 00:30:37,430
In the two days,

381
00:30:38,090 --> 00:30:39,350
she only had sweet potatoes.

382
00:30:43,470 --> 00:30:45,210
Why does she like sweet potatoes?

383
00:31:25,220 --> 00:31:26,600
Are you new here?

384
00:31:30,040 --> 00:31:31,810
I’m Huaiji. What about you?

385
00:31:35,620 --> 00:31:36,850
I’m Luoluo.

386
00:31:37,090 --> 00:31:39,470
Luo from “autumn wind blows in Luoyang”.

387
00:31:41,520 --> 00:31:42,610
What a nice name!

388
00:31:43,620 --> 00:31:44,780
You know poems?

389
00:31:45,270 --> 00:31:46,770
= Luoluo =
I know a lot of poems.

390
00:31:47,790 --> 00:31:48,750
Who taught you?

391
00:31:49,470 --> 00:31:50,290
My mother.

392
00:31:50,290 --> 00:31:51,950
My mother is Lady Shang.

393
00:31:54,120 --> 00:31:54,870
Lady Shang?

394
00:31:55,640 --> 00:31:56,470
Luoluo?

395
00:31:57,790 --> 00:31:59,410
I’ll come to you later.

396
00:32:05,390 --> 00:32:07,480
She’s a naughty girl. Sorry to disturb you.

397
00:32:18,500 --> 00:32:20,310
I was too competitive at a young age.

398
00:32:21,250 --> 00:32:22,870
And I competed with the late Empress.

399
00:32:24,250 --> 00:32:25,180
Later,

400
00:32:25,720 --> 00:32:27,230
we were expelled from the palace.

401
00:32:28,500 --> 00:32:30,040
Then she died.

402
00:32:30,570 --> 00:32:31,960
I was sent here.

403
00:32:33,870 --> 00:32:34,780
By then,

404
00:32:35,670 --> 00:32:37,020
I thought

405
00:32:37,020 --> 00:32:38,360
life was no longer meaningful.

406
00:32:39,450 --> 00:32:40,540
I stayed here, waiting to die,

407
00:32:42,870 --> 00:32:44,760
until I adopted her elder sister.

408
00:32:46,720 --> 00:32:47,960
With a daughter,

409
00:32:48,920 --> 00:32:50,390
everything changed.

410
00:32:52,970 --> 00:32:54,280
Her sister got married.

411
00:32:54,950 --> 00:32:56,200
Then I adopted her.

412
00:33:00,020 --> 00:33:01,190
A dying woman

413
00:33:02,720 --> 00:33:04,580
can get back to life

414
00:33:04,700 --> 00:33:05,730
when she’s a mother.

415
00:33:16,250 --> 00:33:19,530
This year, there have been frequent disasters.

416
00:33:20,550 --> 00:33:24,200
The eclipse, earthquake, and flood.

417
00:33:24,700 --> 00:33:28,110
Crops are ruined and people are poverty-stricken.

418
00:33:28,800 --> 00:33:32,400
Your Majesty, it’s time to restrain yourself.

419
00:33:33,420 --> 00:33:35,720
= Liaozi =
Recently, we hear that

420
00:33:36,450 --> 00:33:38,860
you always drink a lot

421
00:33:39,400 --> 00:33:41,040
and we don’t think that’s appropriate.

422
00:33:47,450 --> 00:33:48,160
Your Majesty.

423
00:33:49,900 --> 00:33:50,720
Your Highness.

424
00:34:02,650 --> 00:34:03,370
Your Highness.

425
00:34:09,370 --> 00:34:11,190
Are you come to check

426
00:34:11,190 --> 00:34:12,400
if I will take less medicine

427
00:34:12,420 --> 00:34:14,000
because it’s bitter?

428
00:34:45,650 --> 00:34:46,610
It tastes good.

429
00:34:48,320 --> 00:34:49,750
Huirou must like it.

430
00:34:49,900 --> 00:34:50,710
Later,

431
00:34:50,850 --> 00:34:52,370
send some to her.

432
00:35:00,150 --> 00:35:01,150
This time,

433
00:35:02,400 --> 00:35:04,220
Huirou comes back for a few days.

434
00:35:06,370 --> 00:35:07,360
Is she happy?

435
00:35:11,150 --> 00:35:12,480
She likes her little sisters.

436
00:35:13,500 --> 00:35:15,580
She often visits Madam Zhou and Madam Dong

437
00:35:15,580 --> 00:35:16,510
to see her sisters.

438
00:35:17,150 --> 00:35:19,680
She has made stuffed toys and hairpins

439
00:35:19,680 --> 00:35:20,700
for them.

440
00:35:27,720 --> 00:35:28,620
Does she

441
00:35:31,300 --> 00:35:32,400
smile again?

442
00:35:44,120 --> 00:35:45,620
I don’t dare to see her.

443
00:35:47,750 --> 00:35:49,350
Whenever she sees me, she asks,

444
00:35:50,050 --> 00:35:51,420
“Where is Huaiji?”

445
00:35:52,050 --> 00:35:53,650
“You didn’t kill him, did you?”

446
00:35:55,020 --> 00:35:57,090
“Have you already killed him?”

447
00:36:02,500 --> 00:36:03,460
In fact,

448
00:36:05,250 --> 00:36:06,600
Prince Consort begged me

449
00:36:08,860 --> 00:36:10,760
to let Huirou see Huaiji

450
00:36:11,520 --> 00:36:13,000
so that she would know he was safe.

451
00:36:15,670 --> 00:36:16,840
Prince Consort is a good boy.

452
00:36:17,900 --> 00:36:19,850
He loves Huirou.

453
00:36:20,520 --> 00:36:21,830
He doesn’t have the heart to see her suffering.

454
00:36:24,200 --> 00:36:25,990
But if censors know that,

455
00:36:26,620 --> 00:36:28,020
they will complain again.

456
00:36:34,820 --> 00:36:36,340
Censors’ complaint...

457
00:36:45,900 --> 00:36:47,820
= About stopping drinking and having more rest =
Again, Sima Guang asked me to reflect on myself

458
00:36:47,820 --> 00:36:49,100
because of disaster.

459
00:36:50,420 --> 00:36:53,740
“Your Majesty, I hear you drink a lot

460
00:36:53,740 --> 00:36:55,100
and give yourself to lust.

461
00:36:55,100 --> 00:36:56,820
You often stay with concubines.”

462
00:36:58,500 --> 00:37:00,220
It makes me confused.

463
00:37:01,140 --> 00:37:03,180
They say I’m a wise emperor.

464
00:37:04,180 --> 00:37:06,420
But in their heart,

465
00:37:06,420 --> 00:37:08,980
I’m muddled, lazy, and addicted to wine and women.

466
00:37:13,900 --> 00:37:14,900
Do you believe it?

467
00:37:15,140 --> 00:37:16,300
Sima Guang and the others

468
00:37:17,780 --> 00:37:19,460
may even think

469
00:37:19,460 --> 00:37:20,860
I’m taking the “aphrodisiac”

470
00:37:20,860 --> 00:37:22,540
offered by some flattering men.

471
00:37:26,850 --> 00:37:28,640
Two little ears.

472
00:37:28,780 --> 00:37:29,540
So cute.

473
00:37:29,540 --> 00:37:31,620
I’ll push it.

474
00:37:32,500 --> 00:37:34,300
Come on. Get in the carriage.

475
00:37:34,540 --> 00:37:35,900
Piggy gets in the carriage.

476
00:37:36,020 --> 00:37:37,420
It’s too big for the carriage.

477
00:37:40,540 --> 00:37:41,540
Here it is.

478
00:37:42,020 --> 00:37:43,060
Take it and enjoy it.

479
00:37:45,780 --> 00:37:46,580
Honey.

480
00:37:47,740 --> 00:37:49,460
What do you want today?

481
00:37:49,660 --> 00:37:51,260
= The Eleventh Princess =
Sweet potatoes. Round sweet potatoes.

482
00:37:55,860 --> 00:37:58,700
Sweet potatoes? Sweet potatoes.

483
00:38:00,500 --> 00:38:01,300
Sweet potatoes.

484
00:38:16,660 --> 00:38:19,010
The other day, you passed out

485
00:38:19,660 --> 00:38:21,220
but didn’t want officials to know.

486
00:38:22,300 --> 00:38:24,660
You cancelled the morning court

487
00:38:24,660 --> 00:38:25,780
with the excuse that you didn’t get up

488
00:38:25,780 --> 00:38:26,860
because of drinking too much the night before.

489
00:38:27,500 --> 00:38:30,100
That’s why censors guessed.

490
00:38:33,940 --> 00:38:36,300
If they knew I was sick,

491
00:38:37,300 --> 00:38:38,100
they would have submitted

492
00:38:38,100 --> 00:38:39,820
ten times more proposals.

493
00:38:41,100 --> 00:38:42,780
They would ask me to designate a crown prince

494
00:38:42,780 --> 00:38:44,260
before I died.

495
00:38:52,980 --> 00:38:54,380
You know me.

496
00:38:56,260 --> 00:38:58,300
I don’t insist on

497
00:38:58,300 --> 00:39:00,340
giving the throne to my own son.

498
00:39:01,420 --> 00:39:03,460
And you know

499
00:39:05,100 --> 00:39:06,940
I’ve made full preparation.

500
00:39:09,860 --> 00:39:11,020
I know.

501
00:39:15,020 --> 00:39:16,420
In your heart,

502
00:39:17,180 --> 00:39:20,020
you care most for our nation and people.

503
00:39:21,740 --> 00:39:23,820
Censors are just too worried.

504
00:39:23,940 --> 00:39:25,740
That’s why they get you wrong.

505
00:39:27,860 --> 00:39:28,820
You...

506
00:39:30,020 --> 00:39:31,620
You’re just unconvinced.

507
00:39:33,220 --> 00:39:34,420
Sure, I am.

508
00:39:34,420 --> 00:39:35,820
I’m absolutely unconvinced.

509
00:39:37,620 --> 00:39:39,420
I can make a good boy from the clan

510
00:39:39,420 --> 00:39:40,180
as the crown prince.

511
00:39:40,180 --> 00:39:40,940
But why...

512
00:39:40,940 --> 00:39:42,180
Why can’t I have a son?

513
00:39:43,580 --> 00:39:44,620
Am I not a wise emperor?

514
00:39:45,380 --> 00:39:46,540
Do I not make benevolent policies?

515
00:39:47,220 --> 00:39:48,580
Do I not care for my people?

516
00:39:50,900 --> 00:39:52,340
If I was kind and virtuous enough,

517
00:39:53,100 --> 00:39:54,540
I should have had a lot of children.

518
00:40:06,420 --> 00:40:07,900
Maybe they’re right.

519
00:40:12,060 --> 00:40:13,740
If I were blessed,

520
00:40:15,700 --> 00:40:17,700
Zuixinglai wouldn’t have died.

521
00:40:20,140 --> 00:40:22,380
If I were blessed,

522
00:40:23,980 --> 00:40:25,180
when Madam Dong was pregnant

523
00:40:25,530 --> 00:40:27,220
three times,

524
00:40:30,460 --> 00:40:32,100
she should have had a son.

525
00:40:37,700 --> 00:40:38,780
Madam Dong

526
00:40:40,440 --> 00:40:42,260
is getting better lately.

527
00:40:43,780 --> 00:40:44,940
She can get out bed.

528
00:40:47,500 --> 00:40:49,420
Huirou visits her little sisters every day.

529
00:40:51,700 --> 00:40:54,220
The ninth princess

530
00:40:55,860 --> 00:40:57,300
can read a little.

531
00:40:58,900 --> 00:41:00,100
The eleventh princess

532
00:41:00,860 --> 00:41:03,180
talks more fluently.

533
00:41:05,980 --> 00:41:07,380
The thirteenth princess.

534
00:41:08,940 --> 00:41:11,980
looks the most like you.

535
00:41:27,260 --> 00:41:28,540
Let’s go see them.

536
00:41:37,300 --> 00:41:38,220
How is she?

537
00:41:39,140 --> 00:41:39,940
How is she?

538
00:41:40,540 --> 00:41:41,940
= Madam Dong =

539
00:41:41,940 --> 00:41:43,100
Go get the physician.

540
00:41:45,580 --> 00:41:46,420
Princess...

541
00:41:46,420 --> 00:41:48,060
When Princess walked to a well,

542
00:41:48,060 --> 00:41:49,740
she stopped and said something.

543
00:41:49,740 --> 00:41:50,460
And then...

544
00:41:50,940 --> 00:41:52,420
then she jumped into the well.

545
00:41:52,460 --> 00:41:54,020
No one else managed to pull her.

546
00:41:54,300 --> 00:41:55,820
Luckily, eunuchs reacted quickly

547
00:41:55,860 --> 00:41:56,900
and saved her from the water.

548
00:41:57,580 --> 00:41:59,460
Huirou. Huirou.

549
00:42:00,860 --> 00:42:01,580
Huirou.

550
00:42:02,900 --> 00:42:03,740
Huirou.

551
00:42:05,700 --> 00:42:07,260
Why did you do that?

552
00:42:13,020 --> 00:42:14,700
Did Li Wei come again?

553
00:42:14,980 --> 00:42:16,220
I’ll kick him out.

554
00:42:16,660 --> 00:42:17,460
Okay?

555
00:42:20,020 --> 00:42:20,860
Huirou?

556
00:42:23,580 --> 00:42:25,340
Princess, be good.

557
00:42:25,700 --> 00:42:26,740
Let’s not get in now.

558
00:42:26,900 --> 00:42:28,340
Many people are in there.

559
00:42:28,700 --> 00:42:30,580
I’m going to see my eldest sister.

560
00:42:30,580 --> 00:42:32,380
I’m going to give her

561
00:42:32,380 --> 00:42:33,740
the best I have.

562
00:42:34,500 --> 00:42:36,940
= The Ninth Princess =
Silly piggy, she doesn’t want that.

563
00:42:36,940 --> 00:42:39,100
Why doesn’t she want that?

564
00:42:39,220 --> 00:42:41,420
You love them.

565
00:42:41,660 --> 00:42:43,780
But she wants Huaiji only.

566
00:42:49,700 --> 00:42:52,940
Father, what is Huaiji?

567
00:43:15,260 --> 00:43:15,940
Father.

568
00:43:16,580 --> 00:43:17,300
Father.

569
00:43:17,900 --> 00:43:18,900
Where is Huaiji?

570
00:43:19,060 --> 00:43:20,580
Is he still alive?

571
00:43:24,580 --> 00:43:28,700
Father, I only want Huaiji for my birthday.

572
00:43:33,180 --> 00:43:34,860
Father, she means

573
00:43:35,060 --> 00:43:37,340
she wants no other gift for her birthday,

574
00:43:37,500 --> 00:43:40,060
